0.000Z"],[18,19,20],"fitness","water","workout",false,"/images/swim-1.png","Water aerobics offers an incredible full-body workout while being gentle on your joints.\n\n![Sun & Swim](/images/swim-1.png)\n\n## Why Water Aerobics?\nThe resistance of water provides strength training while buoyancy reduces impact.\n\n## 30-Minute Routine\nLower body focus, upper body work, and cardio bursts with recovery periods.\n\n## Benefits\nLow-impact joint protection with effective muscle building and cardiovascular fitness.\n\nPerfect for all ages and fitness levels!\n\n![Sun & Swim](/images/swim-2.png)","src/content/blog/water-aerobics-workout.md","cc4e2f58b96e0eb2",{"html":27,"metadata":28},"\u003Cp>Water aerobics offers an incredible full-body workout while being gentle on your joints.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/swim-1.png\" alt=\"Sun &#x26; Swim\">\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"why-water-aerobics\">Why Water Aerobics?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>The resistance of water provides strength training while buoyancy reduces impact.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"30-minute-routine\">30-Minute Routine\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Lower body focus, upper body work, and cardio bursts with recovery periods.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"benefits\">Benefits\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Low-impact joint protection with effective muscle building and cardiovascular fitness.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Perfect for all ages and fitness levels!\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/swim-2.png\" alt=\"Sun &#x26; Swim\">\u003C/p>",{"headings":29,"localImagePaths":40,"remoteImagePaths":41,"frontmatter":42,"imagePaths":45},[30,34,37],{"depth":31,"slug":32,"text":33},2,"why-water-aerobics","Why Water Aerobics?",{"depth":31,"slug":35,"text":36},"30-minute-routine","30-Minute Routine",{"depth":31,"slug":38,"text":39},"benefits","Benefits",[],[],{"title":14,"description":15,"pubDate":43,"tags":44,"draft":21,"image":22},["Date","2026-07-08T09:00:00.000Z"],[18,19,20],[]]